40:00.390 --> 40:01.260
malas saya nak layan awak.

40:06.800 --> 40:07.560
Mi dah masak.

40:10.370 --> 40:10.830
Selamat menjamu selera.

40:10.950 --> 40:11.340
Terima kasih.

40:45.230 --> 40:45.790
[Sibuk?]

40:59.170 --> 40:59.930
[Cuti hari ini.]

41:03.670 --> 41:04.390
[Awak...]

41:17.590 --> 41:19.150
