[Saya juga.]

41:57.750 --> 41:58.770
[Saya bawa dia pergi jumpa awak.]

42:08.830 --> 42:09.240
[Tak payah.]

42:10.210 --> 42:11.090
[Saya datang jenguk dia,]

42:12.020 --> 42:13.150
[di samping jenguk Meng Xiaoshan.]

